name: COREX
description: CoreX Protocol is a Layer-2 platform built on the BNB Smart Chain, offering high-performance scalability infrastructure for DeFi, Web3 E-commerce, DAO governance, and AI applications. CoreX aims to reduce transaction costs, increase processing speed, and deliver a seamless Web3 experience for both retail users and institutions.Strengthening our community governance and preparing for a DAO model is our top priority in the next phase.
